      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a true time-capsule: this vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior boasts a deep-gloss finish enhanced by a professional ceramic coating, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather is supple and retains its new-car fragrance, while every button, screen, and luxury feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a complete, documented service history and a spotless undercarriage. This is an investment-grade vehicle that offers the exact driving experience and aesthetic appeal of a brand-new delivery.",
