    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless, the interior is pristine, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. It\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag! Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728\ud83d\ude97",
